774
00:51:35,735 --> 00:51:37,396
你跟谁说话呢？
Who you talking to?

775
00:51:37,571 --> 00:51:40,301
找我的，明白吗？也有电话找我的
It's for me, okay? I get calls too.

776
00:51:40,474 --> 00:51:41,907
那个人？
That guy?

777
00:51:42,076 --> 00:51:45,568
还是那个，还是那个
Same guy. Same guy.

778
00:51:46,214 --> 00:51:47,579
抱歉
Sorry.

779
00:51:48,616 --> 00:51:52,916
不，没…没关系，我妈妈过去也听我打电话
No. That's... That's okay. My mother used to listen to my calls.

780
00:51:53,087 --> 00:51:55,783
她觉得我什么都做不好
She can't believe I can do anything on my own.

781
00:51:55,957 --> 00:51:57,424
嗯，会改变的
Well, that'll change.

782
00:51:58,160 --> 00:51:59,457
我想也是
I guess.

783
00:51:59,628 --> 00:52:02,654
是的，你看，我们可以给她看些东西
Yeah, but, see, that's something we can show her.

784
00:52:02,831 --> 00:52:05,959
让她知道你能行
That you can do something.

785
00:52:06,134 --> 00:52:09,262
如果你需要，我们可以…我们可以一起干
That we could... We could do that together if you want. I mean...

786
00:52:09,438 --> 00:52:11,702
我是说，我是说我可以帮助你
I mean that I can help you do that.

787
00:52:12,642 --> 00:52:15,270
周一我可以搞到1万2
I can get you 12 by Monday.

788
00:52:15,445 --> 00:52:17,504
1万2太少了，不怎么好
Twelve's weak. Twelve looks bad.

789
00:52:17,680 --> 00:52:19,147
什么意思？
How do you figure that?

790
00:52:19,315 --> 00:52:22,876
他们看看7万5，再看看你，他们想知道 是哪里出了问题
They look at 75 and they look at you and they wonder what the problem is.

791
00:52:23,052 --> 00:52:25,145
而你就给了1万2，这会让他们很紧张的
You say 12. That's gonna make people nervous.

792
00:52:25,321 --> 00:52:28,256
才过了2天，给我点回旋的余地
This was the day before yesterday. Let me get my ducks in order.

793
00:52:28,425 --> 00:52:29,653
车值多少？
What's the car worth?

794
00:52:29,827 --> 00:52:32,022
租的，是公司的
It's a lease. It's the firm's.

795
00:52:32,196 --> 00:52:36,098
那么？你去银行，把公寓抵押了，再申请贷款
So? You go to the bank. You've got the apartment. You refinance.

796
00:52:36,267 --> 00:52:38,895
不行，三个月前我就那么干过了
I can't. I did that three months ago.

797
00:52:39,837 --> 00:52:41,532
你是不是又赌牌去了？
Are you back at the tables?

798
00:52:41,705 --> 00:52:44,640
看来我得重操旧业了，我没什么闲钱了
Like I need that kind of action. I don't have enough going on.

799
00:52:47,812 --> 00:52:49,837
希望你是在和我说笑呢
I hope you're kidding.

800
00:52:50,015 --> 00:52:54,076
要是他发现你用他的钱玩牌，你就完了
If he finds out you're playing cards with his money, there's no dialogue after that.

801
00:52:55,687 --> 00:52:57,678
行行好吧
Do everyone a favor.

802
00:52:57,889 --> 00:53:02,292
快把你的藏宝图拿出来挖宝吧
Get out the treasure map and start digging.

803
00:53:03,062 --> 00:53:04,552
你有一周的时间
You got a week.

804
00:53:05,898 --> 00:53:08,696
- 你好，麦克，还好么？ - 你好，辛迪，我很好
- Hey, Michael. How are you? - Hi, Cindy. I'm good.

805
00:53:08,868 --> 00:53:12,167
请进，他一早上都在打电话，有什么新消息？
Come in. He's been on the phone all morning. What else is new?

806
00:53:12,338 --> 00:53:14,363
我一直在试着让他离开15分钟
I am trying to get him out in 15 minutes.

807
00:53:14,540 --> 00:53:16,974
- 他在楼上么？ - 他把所有的起居室都占了
- Is he upstairs? - He's taken over the living room.

808
00:53:17,144 --> 00:53:19,044
你们俩小家伙干啥呢？快下来
What are you guys doing? Get down here.

809
00:53:19,212 --> 00:53:23,979
索罗约，我告诉过你看好孩子，让他们在楼下玩
Soroyo, I told you to keep an eye on these kids, make sure they're downstairs.

810
00:53:38,499 --> 00:53:39,989
马蒂？
Marty?

811
00:53:42,236 --> 00:53:45,103
你知道他在干什么吗？他在帮他们打官司
You know what he's doing? He's making their case.

812
00:53:45,773 --> 00:53:48,640
我看了他的文件，我看了这个…
I'm going through his files here, I'm reading this...

813
00:53:48,811 --> 00:53:50,676
…他在把案子办成针对U/North的
...he's building a case against U/North.

814
00:53:50,846 --> 00:53:52,837
- 没人会允许他这么做的 - 允许他？
- Nobody's gonna let him do that. - Let him?

815
00:53:53,015 --> 00:53:54,414
谁能阻止他？
Who the hell's gonna stop him?

816
00:53:54,950 --> 00:53:57,612
你知道我刚听说了什么吗？他在给原告打电话
You know what I just heard? He's calling these plaintiffs.

817
00:53:57,786 --> 00:54:01,984
比如作证的那个女的，他现在在联系这些人
This woman from the deposition, he's calling these people now.

818
00:54:02,158 --> 00:54:05,093
他拿到的这些卷宗，简直是他妈的噩梦
He's got these discovery documents. This is a fucking nightmare.

819
00:54:05,261 --> 00:54:08,822
我试着联系他，留不了言，他的答录机满了
I tried him. Can't even leave a message. He's got the machine jammed up.

820
00:54:08,999 --> 00:54:11,524
- 那是他的公文包么？ - 是啊
- Is that his briefcase? - Yeah.

821
00:54:12,102 --> 00:54:13,899
- 怎么了？ - 我们一直在找它
- Why? - We've been looking for it.

822
00:54:14,070 --> 00:54:17,597
我也不知道，它就和他办公室里的 其他破烂一起出现了
I don't know. It came up here with all the other stuff from his office.

823
00:54:17,775 --> 00:54:21,506
你肯定不相信他那儿有多少破烂
You can't believe the crap he's got in here.

824
00:54:22,546 --> 00:54:23,570
我说，马蒂…
Listen, Marty...

825
00:54:25,549 --> 00:54:27,881
…我在这儿欠了点钱
...l'm in a bind here.

826
00:54:29,053 --> 00:54:31,783
我得借点钱，8万块
I need a loan. I need 80 grand.

827
00:54:32,957 --> 00:54:35,289
- 我还以为你都解决了呢 - 还没有
- I thought you were done with that. - It's not that.

828
00:54:35,460 --> 00:54:38,293
不是赌牌欠的，那个不欠了，是餐馆的钱
It's not the cards. It's none of that. It's the restaurant.

829
00:54:38,463 --> 00:54:40,055
8万块
Eighty thousand.

830
00:54:40,232 --> 00:54:41,699
很抱歉突然来打扰你
I'm sorry to jump you like this.

831
00:54:41,867 --> 00:54:44,631
两周来我一直试着和你会面
I've been trying to get a meeting with you for two weeks.

832
00:54:45,404 --> 00:54:48,703
还有不管应不应该，我都知道了合并的事
And I know about the merger, whether I'm supposed to or not.

833
00:54:49,107 --> 00:54:50,802
合并的事还没有定论
There's nothing final on the merger.

834
00:54:50,977 --> 00:54:53,912
嗯，那就是为什么我现在问你 你是我的生活来源
Well, that's why I'm asking you now. You're my meal ticket.

835
00:54:54,080 --> 00:54:56,742
一旦你退出了，就剩我和巴里还有一屋子的 陌生人…
Once you're out, it's me and Barry with strangers...

836
00:54:56,916 --> 00:54:58,816
…我得能解释我究竟干了些什么
...and I'm trying to explain what I do.

837
00:54:58,985 --> 00:55:02,045
所有人都知道你的价值有多大，大家都知道
Everybody knows how valuable you are. Everybody who needs to know.

838
00:55:02,221 --> 00:55:03,882
我都45了，现在还穷得一个子儿也没有
I'm 45 years old and I'm broke.

839
00:55:04,057 --> 00:55:06,753
我冲锋陷阵了12年，什么也没得着
I've been riding shotgun for 12 years and I got no equity.

840
00:55:06,927 --> 00:55:08,519
很抱歉，我觉得心里没底
I'm sorry, I don't feel reassured.

841
00:55:08,695 --> 00:55:10,720
没人让你去开酒吧啊
Nobody told you to go into the bar business.

842
00:55:10,898 --> 00:55:13,458
我开酒吧是为了给自己留条后路啊， 留着养老啊
I only opened it so I'd have something else, a way out.

843
00:55:13,634 --> 00:55:15,295
我不知道原来你这么不开心
I had no idea you were so unhappy.

844
00:55:15,469 --> 00:55:18,495
我跟你说过多少次了，把我调回诉讼团队里
How many times did I ask you to put me back on a litigation team?

845
00:55:18,672 --> 00:55:20,333
- 多少次啊？ - 人人都能出庭辩护
- How many? - Anybody can go to court.

846
00:55:20,507 --> 00:55:21,735
你觉得那样很特别么？
You think that's special?

847
00:55:21,910 --> 00:55:24,572
- 我擅长那个 - 很好，很多人也擅长那个
- I was good at it. - Wonderful. So are a lot of people.

848
00:55:25,046 --> 00:55:28,413
这件事上，你所做的，很不错
At this, what you do, you're great.

849
00:55:28,583 --> 00:55:32,849
看在上帝的份上，你有些东西是别人没有的 你有一个合适的职位
For chrissakes, you got something everybody wants. You have a niche.

850
00:55:33,021 --> 00:55:36,013
你占有一席之地，你为自己挣得了一个 合适的位置
You made a place. You made a niche for yourself.

851
00:55:36,191 --> 00:55:40,252
如果你还恋旧的话…“你该看看我在皇后区 当检察官时干的”
And if it's nostalgia..."You should've seen me when I was a DA back in Queens."

852
00:55:40,429 --> 00:55:43,830
我给你个忠告：忘掉它吧
- Let me give you a serious piece of advice: Leave it there.

853
00:55:43,999 --> 00:55:47,992
上帝不允许你像记忆中的那么好了，我看也是
God forbid you're not as good as you remember. I've seen that happen too.

854
00:55:48,871 --> 00:55:51,396
但我不是来这听忠告的，不是么？
But I didn't come here for advice, did I?

855
00:55:51,974 --> 00:55:55,273
那这算怎么回事？我借给你钱 要不你就不帮我搞定亚瑟？
So this is what? I give you the loan or you don't help out with Arthur?

856
00:55:55,445 --> 00:55:57,037
- 我可没说 - 没说？
- I never said that. - No?

857
00:55:57,214 --> 00:55:58,545
也许你该那么说
Maybe you should have.

858
00:55:58,715 --> 00:56:03,379
我不知道你打算怎么处理这事，但这件事 就像癌症一样
I don't know how you're gonna take care of this, but this, this is cancer.

859
00:56:03,553 --> 00:56:06,716
如果我们不迅速地控制住局面，赶快清理干净的话…
This is something, we don't get it reined in and cleaned up soon...

860
00:56:06,890 --> 00:56:09,017
…那么一切都完了，一切
...everything's vulnerable. Everything.

861
00:56:09,827 --> 00:56:13,160
- 你想跟我说什么？ - 我全靠你了
- What are you telling me? - That I'm counting on you.

862
00:56:13,531 --> 00:56:17,490
我在和你说到下周的这个时候 亚瑟要在掌控之中…
I'm telling you that by this time next week, Arthur will be under control...

863
00:56:17,668 --> 00:56:21,229
…然后大家就都会记得你那无穷的价值的
...and everybody who needs to will have been reminded of your infinite value.

864
00:56:21,405 --> 00:56:22,702
上帝啊，马蒂
Jesus, Marty.

865
00:56:22,974 --> 00:56:24,373
嘿
Hey.

866
00:56:24,543 --> 00:56:26,568
你什么时候变得他妈的这么软弱了？
When did you get so fucking delicate?

867
00:56:27,679 --> 00:56:29,237
我要迟到了
I'm late.

868
00:57:08,889 --> 00:57:11,949
你为什么不找吉奈叔叔请警察来帮忙呢？
Why don't you just call Uncle Gene and get the cops to help you?

869
00:57:12,127 --> 00:57:14,152
不是那么回事
It's not that kind of a problem.

870
00:57:15,797 --> 00:57:18,197
- 我们干这个要多长时间？ - 我不知道
- How much longer are we doing this? - I don't know.

871
00:57:30,213 --> 00:57:34,013
如果他回来取车，你就拨这个电话告诉我
If he comes back to get his car, you call that number and let me know.

872
00:57:34,183 --> 00:57:37,311
- 多谢了，非常感谢 - 好的，不客气
- Thank you very much. I appreciate it. - Okay. You're welcome.

873
00:57:44,695 --> 00:57:47,687
如果我们不是去看电影，你为什么不直说呢？
If we're not gonna get to the movie, why don't you just say so?

874
00:57:47,864 --> 00:57:50,628
- 什么？ - 我要回家
- What? - I wanna go home.

875
00:57:50,801 --> 00:57:52,598
别闹，亨利
Come on, Henry.

876
00:57:56,006 --> 00:57:56,995
等下！
Hold up!

877
00:58:00,044 --> 00:58:01,909
呆在车里，把门锁好
Stay in the car. Lock the door.

878
00:58:03,548 --> 00:58:06,517
亚瑟！亚瑟！
Arthur! Arthur!

879
00:58:06,684 --> 00:58:08,015
等等
Wait up.

880
00:58:08,853 --> 00:58:12,254
麦克，天啊，你吓了我一跳
Michael. Jeez. You scared me.

881
00:58:13,658 --> 00:58:16,388
- 送货去？ - 不，不，不是
- Making a delivery? - No, no, no.

882
00:58:17,229 --> 00:58:19,857
挺搞笑，不是，不是那么回事
Very funny. No, nothing like that.

883
00:58:20,032 --> 00:58:23,627
给，拿一根，拿着，还…还热呢
Here, take one, please. Really. It's... It's still warm.

884
00:58:23,802 --> 00:58:25,429
这是我吃过的最香的面包
It's the best bread I ever tasted.

885
00:58:29,476 --> 00:58:31,205
欢迎回来
So welcome home.

886
00:58:32,379 --> 00:58:35,314
我知道，宾馆的事，很抱歉
I know, the hotel. I'm sorry.

887
00:58:35,482 --> 00:58:37,848
我感觉有点儿压抑
I was beginning to feel a little overwhelmed.

888
00:58:38,018 --> 00:58:39,849
- 你现在感觉好些了么？ - 是啊
- But you're feeling better now? - Yeah.

889
00:58:40,020 --> 00:58:42,511
- 好多了，确实 - 还没好到能给我回电话
- Much better, definitely. - Not enough to call me back.

890
00:58:42,689 --> 00:58:45,920
嗯，那个，在打电话之前，我想…
Well, I was trying to gather my thoughts...

891
00:58:46,093 --> 00:58:49,688
整理好我的思路，就是这么回事
...before I called you, and that's what I was doing.

892
00:58:50,331 --> 00:58:51,730
那件事怎么样？
And how's that going?

893
00:58:51,899 --> 00:58:54,367
很好，非常好，就是…
Yes, it's good, very good. I just...

894
00:58:54,669 --> 00:59:00,073
嗯，就是我需要把思路理得更清晰些 那就是…
Well, I just need to make my thoughts a little bit more precise. That's...

895
00:59:00,241 --> 00:59:01,538
那就是我的目标
That's my goal.

896
00:59:01,710 --> 00:59:05,077
和这感觉一样的是你知道它会怎么发展
As good as this feels, you know where it goes.

897
00:59:05,247 --> 00:59:06,646
不，不，你错了
No. No. You're wrong.

898
00:59:06,815 --> 00:59:09,909
这感觉之所以好，是因为我不知道它会 怎么发展
What makes this feel good is that I don't know where it goes.

899
00:59:11,086 --> 00:59:14,249
我怎么跟你说呢，亚瑟？你听我的吗？
How do I talk to you, Arthur? So you hear me?

900
00:59:14,423 --> 00:59:18,951
像个孩子？像个混球？还是好像一切都好？
Like a child? Like a nut? Like everything's fine?

901
00:59:19,128 --> 00:59:22,894
你有什么秘密？因为我需要你听我说
What's the secret? Because I need you to hear me.

902
00:59:23,066 --> 00:59:25,830
- 嗯，我什么都听的 - 那么听着这个
- Well, I hear everything. - Then hear this.

903
00:59:26,269 --> 00:59:30,228
你需要帮助，在事情无法挽回之前，你需要帮助
You need help. Before this goes too far, you need help.

904
00:59:30,406 --> 00:59:31,634
你的牌很好
You got great cards here.

905
00:59:31,808 --> 00:59:35,141
要是你能把衣服穿好，你爱他妈干什么 就干什么
If you keep your clothes on, you can do any goddamn thing you want.

906
00:59:35,312 --> 00:59:38,543
你想不干了，你就可以不干了 你想烤面包，烤去呗
You want out, you're out. You wanna bake bread, go with God.

907
00:59:38,716 --> 00:59:41,412
这一大堆破事里你就办错了一件…
There's only one wrong answer in this whole goddamn pile...

908
00:59:41,585 --> 00:59:43,348
…但你还护着短儿不承认
...and you've got your arms around it.

909
00:59:43,520 --> 00:59:46,819
- 好吧，我说了我很抱歉 - 你觉得那旅馆很压抑？
- Well, I said I was sorry. - You thought the hotel was overwhelming?

910
00:59:46,990 --> 00:59:49,550
你让这案子难过，他们就会打断你的腿
You piss on this case, they'll cut you off at the knees.

911
00:59:49,728 --> 00:59:52,993
- 我不知道你在说什么 - 我在给你收拾烂摊子
- I don't know what you're talking about. - I'm covering for you.

912
00:59:53,164 --> 00:59:56,656
我跟他们说一切都好，你很好 一切都会好的，大家都很好
I'm telling them everything's fine. You're fine. Everybody's cool.

913
00:59:56,835 --> 01:00:00,066
我到处给人讲“天才的价值”的故事
I'm out running this "price of genius" story to anybody who'll listen.

914
01:00:00,238 --> 01:00:04,470
但今天早上我一起来，就听说你和这个 威斯康星来的姑娘联系上了
And then I wake up this morning and I hear you're calling this girl from Wisconsin...

915
01:00:04,643 --> 01:00:06,508
…还有什么该死的文件和其他一些破烂儿
...messing with documents and whatever else.

916
01:00:06,679 --> 01:00:09,204
- 你怎么知道的？ - 他们掌控着一切
- How can you know that? - They're gonna take everything.

917
01:00:09,382 --> 01:00:12,874
你的合伙身份、你的流通股 他们会吊销你的执照
Your partnership, your equity. They're gonna pull your license.

918
01:00:13,052 --> 01:00:15,213
- 你怎么知道我给安娜打了电话？ - 马蒂告诉我的
- How do you know I called Anna? - Marty told me.

919
01:00:15,388 --> 01:00:19,154
- 那么，他怎么知道的？ - 我不知道，我可没胡扯！
- Well, how does he know? - I don't know. I don't give a shit!

920
01:00:22,863 --> 01:00:24,797
- 你在窃听我的电话 - 天啊，亚瑟
- You're tapping my phone. - Jesus, Arthur.

921
01:00:24,965 --> 01:00:26,830
那么解释一下，告诉我马蒂怎么知道的！
Then explain it. Tell me how Marty knows!

