有医疗补助的，我们都有，我可以给你文件…
It's Medicaid. They're running us in circles. I can pull the file...

1080
01:12:33,670 --> 01:12:35,535
让他走吧，斯蒂芬，他有约会
Let him go, Steph. He's got a date.

1081
01:12:35,705 --> 01:12:37,969
我和一个疯狂律师有约
I've got a date with a maniac attorney.

1082
01:12:38,141 --> 01:12:40,735
- 晚上别工作了，米奇 - 你看起来很疲倦
- Take a night off, Mickey. - You look tired.

1083
01:12:40,912 --> 01:12:42,903
- 我没事，回见 - 好好的
- I'm okay. See you soon. - Be good.

1084
01:12:43,080 --> 01:12:45,310
- 好了，再见 - 再见，亨利
- All right. Bye. - Bye, Hen.

1085
01:12:45,483 --> 01:12:47,178
- 再见，爸爸 - 再见
- Bye, Pop. - Bye.

1086
01:12:57,229 --> 01:12:59,595
- 提米叔叔，你好啊！ - 你怎么样啊，亨利？
- Uncle Timmy, hey! - How you doing, Henry?

1087
01:12:59,765 --> 01:13:01,096
亨利，快上车
Henry, get in the car.

1088
01:13:03,769 --> 01:13:05,202
见到你很高兴，亨利
Good to see you, Hen.

1089
01:13:07,105 --> 01:13:09,869
- 你想要什么？ - 我已经戒酒8天了
- What do you want? - I've been sober eight days now.

1090
01:13:10,877 --> 01:13:14,540
出来见几个面，我想让你知道
Been back at the meetings. I wanted you to know.

1091
01:13:14,714 --> 01:13:16,341
在孩子面前？
In front of the kid?

1092
01:13:16,516 --> 01:13:20,008
米奇，求你了，我知道我曾经有多坏，我发誓
Mickey, please. I know how bad I did, I swear.

1093
01:13:21,020 --> 01:13:24,615
我不知道该怎么走上正轨，我满脑子想的 都是这个
I don't know how to make it right again. It's all I think about.

1094
01:13:25,124 --> 01:13:27,422
我该怎么做？我知道干什么
What do I do? I don't know what to do.

1095
01:13:28,529 --> 01:13:31,054
把轮胎还给斯蒂芬娜
Get Stephanie her tires back.

1096
01:13:36,337 --> 01:13:39,306
- 他哭了？ - 不知道
- Is he crying? - I don't know.

1097
01:13:39,473 --> 01:13:41,304
因为吸了毒，是么？
Because of drugs, right?

1098
01:13:41,475 --> 01:13:43,272
差不多就那玩意儿
That and everything else.

1099
01:14:14,645 --> 01:14:16,112
怎么了？
What?

1100
01:14:18,382 --> 01:14:19,747
你提米叔叔…
Your Uncle Timmy...

1101
01:14:20,417 --> 01:14:25,912
我是说，在他最风光的时候 也没有像你这样坚强
...and I mean this, on his best day, is never as tough as you.

1102
01:14:26,957 --> 01:14:30,120
我不是说他哭了，或者吸毒什么的
I'm not talking about crying or the drugs or anything.

1103
01:14:30,294 --> 01:14:33,388
我是在说他的心，内心里，你明白么？
I'm talking about in his heart, in his heart. You understand me?

1104
01:14:34,465 --> 01:14:38,333
他就会胡诌，吹的天花乱坠的
And all his charming bullshit, this Big Tim, Uncle, Boss bullshit...

1105
01:14:38,503 --> 01:14:40,698
…我知道你爱他，我知道为什么
...and I know you love him, and I know why.

1106
01:14:40,872 --> 01:14:42,669
但当你看见他那熊样…
But when you see him like that...

1107
01:14:42,840 --> 01:14:45,604
…你不必担心，你不会成为那样的人的
...you don't have to worry. That's not how it'll be for you.

1108
01:14:45,778 --> 01:14:48,338
你不会成为那种天天慨叹…
You're not gonna be someone that goes through life...

1109
01:14:48,514 --> 01:14:52,109
…为什么自己老是踩到臭狗屎的人
...wondering why shit keeps falling out of the sky around them.

1110
01:14:52,284 --> 01:14:54,684
我知道，我知道这一点
I know that. I know it.

1111
01:14:54,853 --> 01:14:56,150
明白么？
Okay?

1112
01:15:00,392 --> 01:15:04,556
每次我看着你我都能看出这一点来 我现在就能看到
I see it every time I look at you. I see it right now.

1113
01:15:06,866 --> 01:15:09,596
我不知道你是从哪儿获得的，但你确实有
I don't know where you got it from, but you got it.

1114
01:15:11,304 --> 01:15:12,635
明白么？
Okay?

1115
01:15:25,853 --> 01:15:27,150
喂
Hello?

1116
01:15:37,165 --> 01:15:41,067
邻居过来了，他们在修理楼下的阁楼
The neighbors came by. They're renovating the loft downstairs.

1117
01:15:41,236 --> 01:15:45,866
他们发现有水流从他的盥洗室流到下面
They had water flooding from his bathroom down to their place.

1118
01:15:46,208 --> 01:15:51,510
他的前门、紧急通道，都被他锁得严严实实
His front door, fire escape, he had everything locked up pretty good.

1119
01:15:51,681 --> 01:15:56,015
我的人花了10分钟才进去，还不得不把门砸掉
It took our guys 10 minutes. They had to knock the thing down.

1120
01:15:57,019 --> 01:15:59,954
到处都是药丸
There's pills all over the place.

1121
01:16:00,757 --> 01:16:05,820
完全就是自杀的现场
Just the scene alone is pretty definitive for suicide.

1122
01:16:06,530 --> 01:16:08,930
然后我问了一些最近处理过这种事的…
Then I spoke to some of your partners...

1123
01:16:09,099 --> 01:16:12,694
你的老熟人，因此…
...who ran down these problems he'd been having lately, so...

1124
01:16:15,038 --> 01:16:18,201
- 有遗言么？ - 没有，他们看过了
- Is there a note? - No. They looked.

1125
01:16:18,776 --> 01:16:23,338
可能是个意外或者他本打算写遗言但没写成
It could be an accident or he was gonna write a note and just messed up.

1126
01:16:24,415 --> 01:16:25,712
我能进去么？
Can I get in there?

1127
01:16:25,884 --> 01:16:28,910
他的住处？现在不行，已经封闭了
His place? Not now. It's sealed.

1128
01:16:29,621 --> 01:16:33,785
一旦现场封闭，一切都冻结了，我们会试着 联系他的女儿
Once the seal goes up, it's frozen. We're gonna try and reach his daughter.

1129
01:16:33,958 --> 01:16:37,086
我想她在欧洲，但她就要回来了
I guess she's off in Europe. But she's gotta come in.

1130
01:16:37,730 --> 01:16:40,790
还要等尸检官的毒物报告检测结果
Or the M.E.'s gotta come back with a toxicology report.

1131
01:16:40,966 --> 01:16:44,663
至少要花几周的时间，只能那样了
That's a couple of weeks at least that it's gotta stay like that.

1132
01:16:45,104 --> 01:16:46,469
抱歉
Sorry.

1133
01:16:48,507 --> 01:16:49,974
没事
Sure.

1134
01:16:56,249 --> 01:16:57,238
好吧
Okay.

1135
01:17:01,488 --> 01:17:06,084
我认识你弟弟，我妻子在皇后区那边做事
I know your brother a little. My wife works the 190 out in Queens.

1136
01:17:07,728 --> 01:17:08,888
代我向他问好
I'll tell him hello.

1137
01:17:09,063 --> 01:17:11,088
如果有什么新情况，我会和你联系的
If something comes in, I'll get back to you.

1138
01:17:11,966 --> 01:17:13,331
好的，谢谢你
Yeah. I appreciate it.

1139
01:17:13,501 --> 01:17:15,298
对您的损失感到很难过
I'm sorry for your loss.

1140
01:17:33,789 --> 01:17:36,383
- 麦克 - 杰夫
- Michael. - Jeff.

1141
01:17:36,558 --> 01:17:38,025
这真难过
This is tough.

1142
01:17:38,194 --> 01:17:39,786
是，是啊，他在这儿么？
Yeah, it is. He in here?

1143
01:17:51,342 --> 01:17:53,537
沉默寡言的混球
Dumb son of a bitch.

1144
01:17:54,044 --> 01:17:55,170
多么可怕
What a thing.

1145
01:17:55,346 --> 01:17:57,576
- 稍等 - 我都不知道…
- Hold on. - I don't even know...

1146
01:17:57,748 --> 01:17:59,648
- 真抱歉 - 嗯，没关系
- I'm so sorry. - Yeah. All right.

1147
01:17:59,817 --> 01:18:03,048
我都没机会和他聊聊
I didn't even get a chance to talk to him.

1148
01:18:03,220 --> 01:18:06,678
那个该死的老疯子
That crazy goddamn bastard.

1149
01:18:07,225 --> 01:18:10,217
多大的损失啊，他到底在想什么？
What a waste. What the hell was he thinking?

1150
01:18:10,896 --> 01:18:12,727
马蒂？我得处理一下这事
Marty? I gotta set this up.

1151
01:18:12,898 --> 01:18:14,422
去，去吧
Go. Go.

1152
01:18:15,166 --> 01:18:16,497
你还好吧？
You okay?

1153
01:18:17,235 --> 01:18:18,998
嗯，还好
Yeah, I'm fine.

1154
01:18:20,272 --> 01:18:22,331
来，咱们喝一杯
Come on, let's get you a drink.

1155
01:18:25,177 --> 01:18:29,409
我一直在回味这件事，比如，是不是 我给他的压力太大了？
I just keep replaying all this back. Like, did I push him too hard?

1156
01:18:29,582 --> 01:18:30,810
不可能
Not a chance.

1157
01:18:30,983 --> 01:18:32,780
我一直没法和他沟通
I just couldn't get through to him.

1158
01:18:32,952 --> 01:18:36,115
得了，你把他吓死了？算了吧 那家伙倔得像头牛
What, you scared him to death? Come on. The man was a bull.

1159
01:18:36,589 --> 01:18:40,218
- 不是那样的 - 他后来为什么屈服了？为什么他…？
- Never happened. - Why does he fold, then? Why does he?

1160
01:18:42,262 --> 01:18:44,127
那一定是场意外
It's gotta be an accident.

1161
01:18:44,298 --> 01:18:45,856
不，不可能，亚瑟会没留下便条？
No, no. Arthur without a note?

1162
01:18:46,033 --> 01:18:49,002
他连撒个尿都要写个备忘录呢，一定是意外
He couldn't piss without leaving a memo. Has to be an accident.

1163
01:18:49,169 --> 01:18:51,433
我不相信，我搞不明白
I don't get that. I don't understand that either.

1164
01:18:51,605 --> 01:18:53,835
前一分钟他还打算控制全世界…
One minute he's gonna take on the whole world...

1165
01:18:54,007 --> 01:18:57,033
…12小时之后，他却自行了断了，为什么呢？
...and then 12 hours later, he's sucking down pills. Why?

1166
01:18:57,211 --> 01:18:58,610
为什么？
Why?

1167
01:19:00,048 --> 01:19:03,245
因为所有人都是他妈的不可理喻的，“为什么？”
Because people are fucking incomprehensible. "Why?"

1168
01:19:07,121 --> 01:19:10,579
我认识亚瑟30年了
Thirty years I know Arthur.

1169
01:19:11,060 --> 01:19:12,721
好日子啊
Good years.

1170
01:19:14,263 --> 01:19:18,427
如果我够诚实，我现在的感觉是什么？
And what I feel right now, if I'm honest?

1171
01:19:21,270 --> 01:19:23,761
我说不出来，太糟了
I can't even say, it's so awful.

1172
01:19:24,907 --> 01:19:26,568
你能说的
You can say it.

1173
01:19:29,112 --> 01:19:31,012
我们只不过比他幸运些
We caught a lucky break.

1174
01:19:34,017 --> 01:19:36,315
确实啊，不是么？
We did, didn't we?

1175
01:19:41,024 --> 01:19:44,460
马蒂？我们得去一下办公室
Marty? We need to get up to the office.

1176
01:19:44,628 --> 01:19:46,357
- 他们同意了？ - 原则上
- They accepted? - In principle.

1177
01:19:46,530 --> 01:19:49,363
丹・杰弗瑞要我们半小时内听电话
Don Jeffries wants us on the phone in half an hour.

1178
01:19:49,533 --> 01:19:52,434
我试着解释亚瑟的事，但他们没有什么同情心
I tried to explain about Arthur, but they're short on sympathy.

1179
01:19:52,603 --> 01:19:54,503
等一下，U/North自己处理呢？
Wait a minute. U/North is settling?

1180
01:19:54,672 --> 01:19:58,733
他们看到了一线希望，他们想试试 这是他们的事，我们能干什么？
They see a window. They wanna try. It's their show. What are we gonna do?

1181
01:20:00,479 --> 01:20:03,607
你尽力了，麦克，我们都尽力了
You did what you could, Michael. We all did.

1182
01:20:05,017 --> 01:20:06,348
这是…
It's...

1183
01:20:06,518 --> 01:20:08,179
这就是我们得到的
It's what we got.

1184
01:20:09,321 --> 01:20:12,154
- 你需要送一下么？ - 不，谢了，我很好
- You need a ride? - No, thanks, I'm fine.

1185
01:20:44,959 --> 01:20:45,948
喂
Hello.

1186
01:20:46,127 --> 01:20:48,721
喂，你好，我找安娜・凯泽森
Hello. Hi. I'm looking for Anna Kysersun.

1187
01:20:48,897 --> 01:20:49,989
你是谁？
Who is this?

1188
01:20:50,165 --> 01:20:53,657
麦克・克莱顿，我是纽约的一名律师 我是从亚瑟那里得到你的号码的
Michael Clayton. I'm an attorney in New York. I got your number from Arthur.

1189
01:20:53,835 --> 01:20:56,702
- 你们可真有种阿 - 什么？
- You have got some nerve. - Excuse me?

1190
01:20:56,871 --> 01:21:00,671
你们让她飞到纽约去，还把她一个人留在机场？
You get her all the way to New York City and then leave her at the airport?

1191
01:21:01,077 --> 01:21:02,669
她是个单纯的人
This is not a complicated person.

1192
01:21:02,845 --> 01:21:05,678
这姑娘从来没去过比密尔沃基远的地方
This is a girl who's never been farther than Milwaukee.

1193
01:21:05,848 --> 01:21:07,839
- 等一下，等等 - 不，你等着
- Wait a minute. Now, wait. - No, you wait.

1194
01:21:08,017 --> 01:21:12,249
她明天就要回家了，她回来以后，你们要是再…
She's coming home tomorrow and when she does, if you call here again...

1195
01:21:12,421 --> 01:21:14,719
你是说她现在在纽约么？
Are you telling me she's in New York right now?

1196
01:21:15,191 --> 01:21:17,182
这还是个小姑娘，你听着没有？
This is a young girl, do you hear me?

1197
01:21:17,360 --> 01:21:19,794
她现在就在城里？
She's in the city right now?

1198
01:21:19,963 --> 01:21:21,521
你是什么人？
What kind of people are you?

1199
01:21:21,698 --> 01:21:24,724
听着，等我一会儿，就一会儿
Listen. You just stay on the phone one second. One second.

1200
01:21:57,436 --> 01:21:58,664
安娜
Anna.

1201
01:22:01,073 --> 01:22:02,563
安娜？
Anna?

1202
01:22:03,376 --> 01:22:06,345
我叫麦克・克莱顿，是亚瑟的一个朋友
My name's Michael Clayton. I'm a friend of Arthur's.

1203
01:22:06,513 --> 01:22:09,175
我问了你姐姐，她说你在这儿
I spoke with your sister. She told me you were here.

1204
01:22:10,483 --> 01:22:12,348
请开开门，安娜
Please open the door, Anna.

1205
01:22:23,664 --> 01:22:25,359
你怎么看？
What are you thinking?

1206
01:22:26,167 --> 01:22:31,469
不知道，我望风，你去搜他的车，找点儿线索
I don't know. I'll watch the door. You check his car. Let's get some details.

1207
01:22:34,308 --> 01:22:37,573
他没有详细说是怎么回事
He didn't want to say exactly what it was.

1208
01:22:39,447 --> 01:22:43,281
就说我来了之后，他会来接我…
Just that when I got here, he would pick me up...

1209
01:22:43,451 --> 01:22:45,817
…然后给我看些东西，我会见到…
...and show me, and I would see...

1210
01:22:46,788 --> 01:22:49,655
…能使整件案子翻盘的东西
...that it was something that would win the whole case.

1211
01:22:52,862 --> 01:22:54,727
即使在今天早上…
Even this morning...

1212
01:22:54,897 --> 01:22:56,489
…我是说，我想：
...I mean, I thought:

1213
01:22:58,034 --> 01:23:02,698
“好吧，如果我到了机场没有票的话我就明白了
"Okay, if I get to the airport and the ticket's not there, then I'll know.

1214
01:23:02,872 --> 01:23:07,969
好了，你很蠢，你可以回家了”
Okay, you're stupid, and you can go home now."

1215
01:23:10,581 --> 01:23:15,416
但确实有票，他付过钱了，好像是800块…
But it was there and he paid, like, 800 dollars...

1216
01:23:15,586 --> 01:23:18,248
…一张头等舱
...for a first-class ticket.

1217
01:23:18,422 --> 01:23:19,889
我只是…
And I just...

1218
01:23:23,828 --> 01:23:25,762
我上了飞机
I got on the plane.

1219
01:23:28,533 --> 01:23:30,467
我相信他了
I believed him.

1220
01:23:35,240 --> 01:23:39,904
你有没有觉得他可能在某种程度上来说 感到失望了？
You think maybe he was in some way disappointed?

1221
01:23:40,746 --> 01:23:44,739
这么说吧，他知道你告诉了其他人这一切…
Let's say that he knew that you told somebody else about all of this...

1222
01:23:44,917 --> 01:23:48,353
…然后，我也说不大大好，在某些程度上 他对你那样做感到失望？
...and, I don't know, in some crazy way, he was disappointed by that?

1223
01:23:49,455 --> 01:23:52,356
- 但我没那么做 - 你一定是跟别人说了
- But I didn't. - You must have told somebody else.

1224
01:23:52,524 --> 01:23:54,082
没有
No.

1225
01:23:55,262 --> 01:23:57,423
他让我发誓了
He made me promise.

1226
01:23:58,932 --> 01:24:03,301
你没跟别人讲这件事？一个都没有？
You didn't tell anybody else about this? Not one other person?

1227
01:24:04,437 --> 01:24:05,836
没有
No.

1228
01:24:10,611 --> 01:24:13,546
他其实是真疯了，不是么？
He really was crazy, wasn't he?

1229
01:24:26,295 --> 01:24:29,162
- 你是说这个么？ - 让我看看
- You talking about this? - Let me see.

1230
01:24:30,666 --> 01:24:32,327
- 你知道这是什么吗？ - 知道
- You know what that is? - Yeah.

1231
01:24:33,268 --> 01:24:36,328
你就说帮个“小忙”，这可比“小忙”大多了
You said a favor. That's more than a favor.

1232
01:24:36,505 --> 01:24:38,666
好了，没人知道这是从哪儿来的
Well, nobody's gonna know where it came from.

1233
01:24:40,042 --> 01:24:42,476
- 是你那事耽搁了么？ - 你什么意思？
- Are you that jammed up? - What are you talking about?

1234
01:24:42,645 --> 01:24:45,273
谁需要这玩意儿？是餐馆的事，是吧？
Who asked for this? It's the restaurant, right?

1235
01:24:45,448 --> 01:24:47,939
是你的某个债主么？“给我搞个封条”
One of these guys you owe? "Get me a seal."

1236
01:24:48,117 --> 01:24:49,744
你真的想知道么？
You really wanna know?

1237
01:26:07,068 --> 01:26:09,298
这事越来越有意思了
This just gets better and better.

1238
01:26:10,938 --> 01:26:12,530
我们干点儿什么呢？
What are we doing?

1239
01:27:58,200 --> 01:28:00,200
“最佳打印”委托印刷清单

1240
01:28:14,203 --> 01:28:15,227
别动！
Freeze!

1241
01:28:15,404 --> 01:28:18,134
呆着别动，你个混蛋！别动！
Right there, asshole! Don't move!

1242
01:28:18,307 --> 01:28:20,571
- 好吧，我没恶意，我是个朋友！ - 举起手来！
- It's all right, I'm a friend! - Get your hands up!

1243
01:28:20,743 --> 01:28:23,268
快把手举起来！快点儿！
Get your hands up now! Now!

1244
01:28:23,446 --> 01:28:25,380
- 你手里是什么？ - 是本书
- What's in your hand? - It's a book.

1245
01:28:25,549 --> 01:28:28,416
放下！快放下！快点儿！
Drop it! Drop it, now! Drop it!

1246
01:28:28,585 --> 01:28:31,884
- 转过来，慢点儿 - 好的，好的，转了
- Turn around. Slowly. - All right. All right. Okay.

1247
01:28:32,055 --> 01:28:33,886
- 这儿还有谁？ - 没别人了
- Who else is here? - Nobody.

1248
01:28:34,057 --> 01:28:36,491
- 我在问你，这儿还有谁？ - 没有别人了！
- I said, who else is here? - Nobody's here!

1249
01:28:36,660 --> 01:28:38,059
查一下那边
Check in there.

1250
01:28:38,863 --> 01:28:42,162
你要是敢动，就打爆你的头
You move, I'll take your head off.

1251
01:29:12,031 --> 01:29:16,468
现在我欠这家伙和我部门里他那混蛋老婆的情
Now I owe this scumbag and his wife... Who's a complete piece of shit in my unit.

1252
01:29:16,636 --> 01:29:18,729
- 现在我把命都押上了 - 很抱歉
- Now I owe them both my balls. - I'm sorry.

1253
01:29:18,905 --> 01:29:20,896
- 你了解我的 - 不是说“没人会知道的”么
- You know I am. - "Nobody will know it's me."

1254
01:29:21,074 --> 01:29:24,134
他们要是发现了怎么办，发现是我 给的你那该死的…
You know what happens they don't bury this, that I gave you this?

1255
01:29:24,311 --> 01:29:25,676
很糟糕，我知道了
It's bad. I know it.

1256
01:29:25,846 --> 01:29:28,906
我还有18个月就工作满20你年了 你的举动让我的退休金岌岌可危
I'm 18 months away from my 20. You just put my pension in jeopardy.

1257
01:29:29,083 --> 01:29:31,051
- 你终于说到“重点”了 - 那不是什么重点！
- You made your point. - It's not a point!

1258
01:29:31,218 --> 01:29:33,584
- 谁报的警？ - 什么？
- Who called 911? - What?

1259
01:29:33,887 --> 01:29:36,822
大楼空无一人，我是轻手轻脚的 我都没呆多长时间
The building was empty. I was quiet. I wasn't there very long.

1260
01:29:36,991 --> 01:29:39,425
谁叫警察来的？这些你有没有想过这事…？
Who called it in? Does that make sense to you...?

1261
01:29:39,593 --> 01:29:41,151
这事结了
This never happened.

1262
01:29:42,464 --> 01:29:44,489
你让警察觉得你是个律师
You got these cops thinking you're a lawyer.

1263
01:29:44,666 --> 01:29:46,725
你让律师觉得你是个警察
You got these lawyers thinking you're a cop.

1264
01:29:46,901 --> 01:29:51,031
你把大伙都骗了，不是么？除你之外所有人
You got everybody fooled, don't you? Everybody but you.

1265
01:29:51,206 --> 01:29:53,299
你很清楚自己是个什么东西
You know exactly what you are.

1266
01:30:06,922 --> 01:30:08,446
我们给你打过6次电话
We tried calling you six times.

1267
01:30:08,624 --> 01:30:10,751
但你的答录机一定是坏了还是怎么的
But your machine must be busted or something.

1268
01:30:12,596 --> 01:30:14,086
这是我们最好的技术
We gave it our best shot.

1269
01:30:15,432 --> 01:30:17,923
我们的红色封面用完了，库存只有2000…
We ran out of red covers. We only had 2000 in stock...

1270
01:30:18,101 --> 01:30:19,966
…因此剩下的1000我们用了蓝色的
...so we did the other thousand in blue.

1271
01:30:26,209 --> 01:30:28,209
（内部使用） 北地联合克林泰特除草剂内部研究备忘录229号

1272
01:30:41,392 --> 01:30:42,882
没什么问题吧？
Is everything all right?

1273
01:30:43,062 --> 01:30:44,290
啊，没问题
It's fine, yeah.

1274
01:30:44,997 --> 01:30:48,057
嗯，你开车了么？因为后面还有25箱…
You have a van or something? Because I have 25 boxes back there...

1275
01:30:48,233 --> 01:30:51,293
帮我个忙，看好它们
Do me a favor. Hang on to them.

1276
01:30:51,470 --> 01:30:53,700
我下周回来把这些都拉走
I'll come back and pick everything up next week.

1277
01:30:53,872 --> 01:30:55,931
- 真的么？谢了，伙计 - 好的
- Seriously? Thanks, man. - Yeah.

1278
01:31:16,497 --> 01:31:17,862
喂
Hello.

1279
01:31:22,937 --> 01:31:26,236
丹，你们先走，我随后就到
Don. You go ahead. I'll catch up to you.

1280
01:31:26,807 --> 01:31:28,104
什么？
What?

1281
01:31:35,517 --> 01:31:37,678
你认识麦克・克莱顿么？
Do you know Michael Clayton?

1282
01:31:37,853 --> 01:31:39,343
认识，怎么了？
Yeah, why?

1283
01:31:39,521 --> 01:31:41,284
我们遇到了新情况
We have a situation.

1284
01:32:01,077 --> 01:32:02,635
嘿，他们找到你了吗？
Hey, did they find you?

1285
01:32:02,813 --> 01:32:05,839
- 谁找我？ - 马蒂，我想他们还在
- Who? - Marty. I don't think they've gone in yet.

1286
01:32:14,024 --> 01:32:15,355
马蒂
Marty.

1287
01:32:15,692 --> 01:32:18,889
你电话关机了，好多事都找不着你
Your phone's off. There's too much going on for your phone to be off.

1288
01:32:19,063 --> 01:32:21,054
- 我要单独聊聊 - 你看，那个，我们要晚了…
- I need a minute. - Yeah, well, we're late...

1289
01:32:21,232 --> 01:32:22,859
我们昨天晚上还没做完呢
We never got to finish last night.

1290
01:32:23,034 --> 01:32:25,161
你是最后走的吗？看起来气色很差
Did you close the place? You look like hell.

1291
01:32:25,336 --> 01:32:28,396
- 不是，你走之后我就走了 - 如果是那样的话
- No, I left right after you left. - Lf you say so.

1292
01:32:28,573 --> 01:32:31,269
我们忙了一晚上，我们必须发表一项声明
We've been here all night. We had to make an announcement.

1293
01:32:31,442 --> 01:32:34,707
简！我需要那个，给我个信封
Jean! I need the thing, the envelope.

1294
01:32:34,880 --> 01:32:38,077
我本想让你加入进来，但找不到你 我只好做了决定
I wanted your input. I couldn't get you. I had to pull the trigger.

1295
01:32:38,250 --> 01:32:41,185
我让鲍勃・奈斯特和金，可能是用错了
I put Bob Nast and Kim, probably a mistake.

1296
01:32:41,353 --> 01:32:44,686
他们打算这周末举办一个追悼仪式
They're gonna pull together a memorial service by the end of the week.

1297
01:32:44,857 --> 01:32:47,121
我跟他们说了需要帮忙就找你
I told them to call you if they need any help.

1298
01:32:47,626 --> 01:32:50,390
不、不，不是，另一个，另一个
No, no, no. The other one. The other one.

1299
01:32:50,964 --> 01:32:53,262
我们今早给你开了张支票
So we cut you a check this morning.

1300
01:32:53,433 --> 01:32:56,732
但有些附加条件，巴里…
There's some strings attached. And Barry...

1301
01:32:56,903 --> 01:33:01,033
这事没商量，巴里必须参与进来
There's no way around this, Barry's gonna have to be involved.

1302
01:33:04,812 --> 01:33:07,246
如果亚瑟是在追查某件事情呢？
What if Arthur was on to something?

1303
01:33:07,415 --> 01:33:09,076
你什么意思？追查什么？
What do you mean? On to what?

1304
01:33:09,250 --> 01:33:12,117
U/North，如果他没疯？如果他是对的呢？
U/North. What if he wasn't crazy? What if he was right?

1305
01:33:12,286 --> 01:33:14,447
什么对了？我们站错了队？
Right about what? That we're on the wrong side?

1306
01:33:14,622 --> 01:33:17,056
站错了队，走错了路，一切，一切都不对
Wrong side, wrong way, everything, all of it.

1307
01:33:17,225 --> 01:33:20,160
这事新鲜么？这案子从第一天起就臭不可闻
This is news? This case reeked from day one.

1308
01:33:20,329 --> 01:33:22,320
你都呆了15年了，还要我告诉你我们是 怎么赚钱的吗？
I gotta tell you how we pay the rent?

1309
01:33:22,497 --> 01:33:25,227
他们会怎么做？如果他把事实公之于众呢？
What would they do? What would they do if he went public?

1310
01:33:25,400 --> 01:33:28,801
他们会怎么做？你他妈的傻了吧？ 他们已经这么做了
What would they do? Are you fucking soft? They're doing it.

1311
01:33:28,971 --> 01:33:31,405
如果我们不能在24小时内彻底解决这事…
We don't straighten the settlement out in 24 hours...

1312
01:33:31,573 --> 01:33:33,632
…他们就会拒绝支付900万的律师费
...they're gonna withhold $9 million in fees.

1313
01:33:33,809 --> 01:33:36,778
然后他们还会公布亚瑟在密尔沃基 跳脱衣舞的录像
Then they'll pull out the video of Arthur doing his flashdance.

1314
01:33:36,946 --> 01:33:38,675
他们会起诉我们玩忽职守
They'll sue us for legal malpractice.

1315
01:33:38,848 --> 01:33:42,511
除了这些之外，与伦敦的合并案也会告吹…
Except there won't be anything to win because the London merger will be dead...

1316
01:33:42,685 --> 01:33:45,347
…大伙就只能回家喝西北风去了
...and we'll be selling off the goddamn furniture.

1317
01:33:45,822 --> 01:33:47,517
这是8万块
That's 80.

1318
01:33:48,024 --> 01:33:49,821
我们管它就叫奖金
We're calling it a bonus.

1319
01:33:50,660 --> 01:33:52,685
你以现在的年薪续约3年
Three-year contract at your current numbers.

1320
01:33:52,863 --> 01:33:54,490
那奖金是将给那个的
That's assuming this all works out.

1321
01:33:54,665 --> 01:33:55,825
你现在就办了？
You're doing this now?

1322
01:33:57,501 --> 01:34:00,834
我说，我同意这么办，好吧？但有条件的
Look, I agreed to this, okay? But there's rules now.

1323
01:34:01,005 --> 01:34:03,872
你想要合同，就得签订一份保密协议
You want the contract, you sign a confidentiality agreement.

1324
01:34:04,041 --> 01:34:06,134
协议内容不能更改，同时具有追溯效力
It's gonna be bulletproof and retroactive.

1325
01:34:06,310 --> 01:34:08,039
因为马蒂这人很友善，不愿意说…
Because Marty's too nice to say it...

1326
01:34:08,213 --> 01:34:12,013
…但就你对这地方的了解，客户和 在这儿工作的员工…
...but with all you know about this place, the clients and people who work here...

1327
01:34:12,183 --> 01:34:14,743
…都会对你要价8万块感到有点儿奇怪
...it makes it a little weird when you ask for 80 grand.

1328
01:34:15,420 --> 01:34:18,116
我要是勒索别人，第一个先找你…
If I was gonna shake anybody down, I'd come to you...

1329
01:34:18,290 --> 01:34:20,952
…而且肯定不会只要8万块 这是你的意思还是他的？
...and it wouldn't be for 80 grand. Is this him or you?

1330
01:34:21,126 --> 01:34:23,720
- 如果我错了，我道歉 - 你他妈的完全错了
- Lf I'm wrong, I apologize. - You're way the fuck wrong.

1331
01:34:23,896 --> 01:34:25,124
随你便好了
So there you go.

1332
01:34:25,298 --> 01:34:26,959
够了，你俩，行了吧？
Enough. Okay? Everybody.

1333
01:34:27,833 --> 01:34:29,994
他是个混蛋，但他清楚地知道这一点
He's an asshole, but he knows it.

1334
01:34:30,403 --> 01:34:33,668
你呢，是公认的（混蛋），好了吧？ 大家都高兴了？
And you're on the record. Okay? Everybody happy?

1335
01:34:34,307 --> 01:34:37,003
- 丹・杰弗瑞来了 - 我们就到
- Don Jeffries is here. - We're on the way.

1336
01:34:37,810 --> 01:34:41,906
和鲍勃・奈斯特联系一下，看看 他们需要帮忙不
Call Bob Nast. Just see if they need help with this thing.

1337
01:34:45,485 --> 01:34:46,850
欢迎回来
You're welcome.

1338
01:35:39,743 --> 01:35:42,109
你说是1万2，这可是7万5啊
You said 12. This is 75.

1339
01:35:42,279 --> 01:35:44,440
嗯，别激动，你要来一杯吗？
Well, don't get too excited. You want a drink?

1340
01:35:44,615 --> 01:35:46,480
不，我上班呢
No. I'm working.

1341
01:35:48,919 --> 01:35:52,446
现在我们扯平了，那么，不用干别的了
So we're square, then. No bad blood.

1342
01:35:52,623 --> 01:35:54,318
你只是在尽自己的职责罢了
You're just doing your job.

1343
01:35:54,492 --> 01:35:55,959
是啊
That's right.

1344
01:35:56,894 --> 01:35:58,623
保重，盖比
Take it easy, Gabe.

1345
01:35:59,631 --> 01:36:00,996
你也一样
Michael.

1346
01:36:12,744 --> 01:36:14,177
不跟
Check.

1347
01:36:16,015 --> 01:36:17,277
不跟
Check.

1348
01:36:17,617 --> 01:36:20,347
- 不跟 - 半注，两百
- Check. - Half the pot. Two hundred.

1349
01:36:20,520 --> 01:36:21,817
两百胜
Two hundred to go.

1350
01:36:59,194 --> 01:37:00,957
那么，餐馆现在怎么样了
So, what happened with the bar?

1351
01:37:01,130 --> 01:37:03,155
看来你经营的不善啊，哈？
You just had to be a rock star, huh?

1352
01:37:25,655 --> 01:37:28,419
你干什么？你才刚来
What are you doing? You just got here.

1353
01:37:28,592 --> 01:37:30,526
这哥们儿才玩了9手，这就走了
Guy plays nine hands, walks away.

1354
01:37:30,694 --> 01:37:34,858
我把你吓跑了？我干了什么？ 是我把你吓跑了吗？
I scare you away? What did I do? Did I scare you away?

1355
01:38:10,637 --> 01:38:11,695
快走
Get out.

1356
01:38:13,072 --> 01:38:15,199
快离开车子
Get out of the car now.

1357
01:38:16,943 --> 01:38:17,932
- 沃尔特？ - 麦克
- Walter? - Michael.

1358
01:38:18,111 --> 01:38:20,306
- 麦克，谢天谢地，总算找到你 - 嗯
- Michael. Thank God you're there. - Yeah.

1359
01:38:24,718 --> 01:38:26,652
你还有8秒…
You have eight...

1360
01:38:27,555 --> 01:38:30,285
…6、5…
...six, five...

1361
01:38:30,457 --> 01:38:32,789
…4、3…
...four, three...

1362
01:38:32,960 --> 01:38:34,587
快走
Get out of the car.

1363
01:38:38,033 --> 01:38:41,059
- 告诉他不要接任何电话了 - 好的，你会去吧？
- Tell him to stay off the phone. - All right. But you're on it?

1364
01:38:41,670 --> 01:38:43,103
我没被发现吧？
Am I clean?

1365
01:38:43,271 --> 01:38:44,499
接着走
Just keep walking.

1366
01:38:44,673 --> 01:38:46,903
收到，我没被发现吧？
You copy. Am I clean?

1367
01:38:47,108 --> 01:38:50,100
走就是了，他正朝他的车走去
Just keep moving. He's walking to the car.

1368
01:38:50,645 --> 01:38:54,206
你只要在路上就行了，我会给你带来更多的细节
- To let him know you're on the way. I'll get back to you with the details.

1369
01:38:54,383 --> 01:38:56,817
- 给我2分钟 - 我马上开车去
- Just give me two minutes. - I'll be in the car.

1370
01:39:00,523 --> 01:39:03,959
我没安完，是放上了，但不知道能不能用
I didn't finish. It's in, but I don't know.

1371
01:39:32,123 --> 01:39:35,684
不是很好，有点儿杂波，他就在前边，但是…
It's loose. I got a pulse. He's up there somewhere, but...

1372
01:39:37,462 --> 01:39:39,396
我来看看能不能增强下信号
Let's find a way to boost the signal.

1373
01:39:46,972 --> 01:39:50,169
- 我不知道沃尔特给了你什么承诺… - 一位天才员工！
- I don't know what Walter promised you... - A miracle worker!

1374
01:39:50,342 --> 01:39:53,573
沃尔特在电话里是这么说的，20分钟前 原话要听么，啊？
That's Walter on the phone, 20 minutes ago. Direct quote, okay?

1375
01:39:53,746 --> 01:39:55,577
“挺住，我会派一个天才来帮助你”
"I'm sending you a miracle worker."

1376
01:39:55,749 --> 01:39:57,410
- 喔，那他说错了 - 哪儿说错了？
- Well, he misspoke. - About what?

1377
01:39:57,584 --> 01:40:01,111
关于你是公司的救火员那部分？ 还是你根本就不在行?
About the fact that you're the firm's fixer? Or that you're any good at it?

1378
01:40:06,893 --> 01:40:08,827
我们走，有信号了
We're up. Just got a signal.

1379
01:40:32,688 --> 01:40:35,054
对面路上没有车过来，他在干什么？
There's nothing back this way. What's he doing?

1380
01:40:35,223 --> 01:40:36,417
也许他迷路了
Maybe he's lost.

1381
01:40:36,591 --> 01:40:38,388
- 等一下 - 他来了
- Wait a minute. - That's him.

1382
01:40:41,731 --> 01:40:42,959
他一个人，是吧？
He was alone, right?

1383
01:40:43,132 --> 01:40:45,930
- 是，我觉得是 - 确定点儿，是还是不是？
- Yeah, I think so. - Call it, yes or no?

1384
01:40:48,371 --> 01:40:49,998
我们得转回去
We gotta turn around.

1385
01:41:20,238 --> 01:41:21,865
什么情况？
Talk to me.

1386
01:41:22,040 --> 01:41:23,598
有点儿乱
It's strobing.

1387
01:41:23,775 --> 01:41:26,175
不，走得对，我想我们走得对，接着开
No, we're good. I think we're good. Just keep going.

1388
01:41:41,994 --> 01:41:43,586
不，他转弯了，不知道为什么他转弯了
No, he turned. Somehow he turned.

1389
01:41:43,763 --> 01:41:45,128
- 哪儿？ - 他在…
- Where? - He took...

1390
01:41:45,632 --> 01:41:47,600
- 他转左了 - 哪儿有左啊
- He took a left. - I don't have a left.

1391
01:41:57,577 --> 01:42:00,512
- 东面，他在东南面 - 什么，我们跟丢了？
- East. He's southeast. - What, so we missed it?

1392
01:42:00,681 --> 01:42:02,808
- 可能是图像有问题 - 别着急
- Or the grid is wrong. - Hang on.

1393
01:42:12,994 --> 01:42:15,690
- 我们得回到第一下 - 第一下什么？哪算第一下？
- We gotta go back to one. - One is what? Where's our one?

1394
01:42:15,898 --> 01:42:18,890
直走半英里，一直开，开就是了
Half a mile straight ahead. Just keep driving. Just go.

1395
01:42:25,774 --> 01:42:28,402
现实我们接近了，但那是西面，不是东边
It says we're closing. But that's west. It can't be west.

1396
01:42:28,577 --> 01:42:29,635
信号还是图像的为问题？
The signal or the grid?

1397
01:42:29,812 --> 01:42:32,542
- 可能都有，减弱了 - 该死的
- It's both. It just keeps dropping out. - Goddamn it.

1398
01:43:23,769 --> 01:43:25,236
把电话给我
Give me the cell.

1399
01:43:27,773 --> 01:43:29,468
我们的信号很好
Our signal's good.

1400
01:45:07,379 --> 01:45:08,641
怎么了？
What?

1401
01:45:11,284 --> 01:45:12,979
谢了，米奇
Thanks, Mickey.

1402
01:45:13,152 --> 01:45:14,813
带我离开这儿
Just get me out of here.

1403
01:45:22,528 --> 01:45:26,259
我要这个的会议时间安排表，越快越好 最晚周四
I wanna get a meeting scheduled on this, soon as we can. Thursday at the latest.

1404
01:45:26,433 --> 01:45:30,062
我觉得我们得找个来自裁决组的人 麦克戴尔可以…
I think we should have someone from the equity group there. Maybe McDonnell...

1405
01:45:30,237 --> 01:45:31,727
- 嗯？ - 你听说了么？
- Yeah? - Did you hear?

1406
01:45:31,905 --> 01:45:34,430
- 是啊，听说了，U/North结案了 - 不是，是麦克・克莱顿的事
- Yeah, yeah. They closed U/North. - No. Michael Clayton.

1407
01:45:34,875 --> 01:45:35,933
什么？
What?

1408
01:45:36,110 --> 01:45:39,011
汽车炸弹，远郊，今天早晨，他被杀了
Car bomb. Upstate. This morning. He was killed.

1409
01:45:40,047 --> 01:45:41,071
什么？
What?

1410
01:45:42,751 --> 01:45:44,582
天啊
Holy shit.

1411
01:45:58,768 --> 01:46:03,705
U/North公司依然坚持认为这场诉讼是…
It has been and it remains the U/North position...

1412
01:46:03,873 --> 01:46:07,969
证据不足而且毫无道理可言的
...that this lawsuit is baseless and without merit.

1413
01:46:08,144 --> 01:46:12,205
基于原告方要求支付超过30亿美元的赔偿金…
Our reluctance to negotiate was anchored by this belief...

1414
01:46:12,382 --> 01:46:17,547
…我们的态度和以前一样，甚至更坚决…
...and reinforced by the plaintiffs' demand for settlement...

1415
01:46:17,721 --> 01:46:20,281
…不愿谈判
...in excess of 3 billion dollars.

1416
01:46:20,457 --> 01:46:23,915
但今天我们聚集在这里…
The reason that we are all here today is...

1417
01:46:24,094 --> 01:46:27,962
…是因为本案的一些关键因素已经发生了变化
...that several key elements in the case have changed.

1418
01:46:28,966 --> 01:46:33,403
你们手中都有一份计划中的一揽子解决方案…
You all have a tentative proposal packet...

1419
01:46:34,005 --> 01:46:37,964
…上面标出了细节，关键之处在于这点：
...which outlines the details, but the bottom line is this:

1420
01:46:38,142 --> 01:46:40,906
在过去的几个月里，有消息指出…
Over the past several months we had gotten word...

1421
01:46:41,079 --> 01:46:44,412
…原告的耐心开始不足…
...that the plaintiffs were growing impatient...

1422
01:46:44,583 --> 01:46:48,417
…他们正在修改要求赔偿金的数目
...and were in the process of revising their settlement numbers.

1423
01:46:48,921 --> 01:46:50,388
我们也了解到…
We also learned...

1424
01:46:50,556 --> 01:46:54,492
…原告的律师费上限为32%…
...that the plaintiffs' attorneys' fees were capped at 32 percent...

1425
01:46:54,660 --> 01:46:56,753
…最高4亿美元…
...up to 400 million dollars...

1426
01:46:57,196 --> 01:47:01,428
…超过的部分，律师费将降为24%
...above which, their fees dropped to 24 percent.

1427
01:47:01,601 --> 01:47:06,163
因此我们知道这种两难的境地让他们…
So we knew that there would be this motivational dead zone for them...

1428
01:47:06,339 --> 01:47:07,670
…止步不前
...in the middle there.

1429
01:47:08,441 --> 01:47:10,136
最后…
Finally...

1430
01:47:10,310 --> 01:47:14,644
…我们的财务部门告知我们他们计算出了
...our finance team informed us that they had run the numbers...

1431
01:47:14,815 --> 01:47:16,646
…赔偿金及税款的总额…
...and that the tax benefit...

1432
01:47:16,817 --> 01:47:20,048
…如果我们能将赔偿金控制在6亿美元以下…
...provided that we bring the settlement in under 600 million...

1433
01:47:20,221 --> 01:47:22,655
…在这一财政年度内…
...and within this fiscal year...

1434
01:47:22,823 --> 01:47:28,693
…公司业绩就可以弥补赔偿金带来的损失
...that the write-off on this settlement would essentially pay for itself.

1435
01:47:29,196 --> 01:47:33,394
你们面前的一揽子解决方案，就我看来…
The package that you have before you represents, in my judgment...

1436
01:47:33,835 --> 01:47:38,636
…是公司在目前情况下的最好选择
...the strongest possible position for our company under the circumstances.

1437
01:47:38,807 --> 01:47:40,502
同时，作为首席顾问…
And, as chief counsel...

1438
01:47:40,675 --> 01:47:43,940
…我建议你们通过这一方案
...it is my recommendation that this proposal be confirmed.

1439
01:47:45,013 --> 01:47:48,540
谢谢你，凯伦，我们需要几分钟时间来 讨论一下这个问题
Thank you, Karen. If you just give us a few minutes to talk about it.

1440
01:47:48,718 --> 01:47:50,982
好的，我在外面等
Certainly. I'll be right outside.

1441
01:47:53,389 --> 01:47:54,378
嗯…
Well...

1442
01:48:17,514 --> 01:48:19,345
里面情况怎么样？
How'd it go in there?

1443
01:48:22,387 --> 01:48:24,582
吓坏了吧，哈？
Pretty freaky, huh?

1444
01:48:24,756 --> 01:48:27,725
你看见亚瑟了么？他就在附近出没
Did you see Arthur? He's wandering around here somewhere.

1445
01:48:30,261 --> 01:48:33,526
我开玩笑呢，放松点儿
I'm kidding. Lighten up.

1446
01:48:35,100 --> 01:48:38,797
你收到这个了吗？这备忘录写的不错 虽然年头久了点儿，但内容很好
You got one of these? It's a great memo. It's an oldie but a goodie.

1447
01:48:41,974 --> 01:48:43,441
我让你心跳加速了，是不是？
Got your heart racing, don't I?

1448
01:48:43,609 --> 01:48:45,736
我不知道你这样做是想干什么
I don't know what it is you think you're doing.

1449
01:48:45,911 --> 01:48:47,276
你觉得我这样做是想干什么？
What do you think I'm doing?

1450
01:48:47,446 --> 01:48:49,243
案子结了，我们和解了
The suit's over. We have a deal.

1451
01:48:49,416 --> 01:48:52,112
不管那是什么，现在都没用了
Whatever that is, it's meaningless at this point.

1452
01:48:52,285 --> 01:48:55,948
你这么认为？这样啊，我还以为你只是 提出一个建议方案呢
You think? I must have gotten it wrong. I thought you had a tentative proposal.

1453
01:48:56,122 --> 01:48:58,317
我还没想到这些钱都是你给的呢
I didn't realize you'd signed all those checks.

1454
01:48:58,491 --> 01:49:01,790
这是个累赘，我有上千本，我拿它们怎么办？
That's a drag. I got a thousand of these. What am I gonna do with them?

1455
01:49:01,962 --> 01:49:03,293
我要给马蒂打电话
I'm calling Marty.

1456
01:49:03,463 --> 01:49:05,829
好，好啊，打吧，那会是个很好的开始
Good. Good. Do it. That's a great place to start.

1457
01:49:06,000 --> 01:49:08,798
让我们看看是谁告诉他亚瑟和安娜・凯泽森联系
Let's find out who told him Arthur was calling Anna Kysersun.

1458
01:49:08,970 --> 01:49:10,801
让我们看看是谁窃听的电话
Let's find out who tapped those phones.

1459
01:49:10,972 --> 01:49:14,772
这本备忘录，我对其真实性有异议 我强烈怀疑…
This memorandum, even if it's authentic, which I doubt, I highly doubt...

1460
01:49:14,942 --> 01:49:18,378
- 我知道你对亚瑟做了些什么 - 这是受保护的文件，它属于U/North公司
- I know what you did to Arthur. - It's protected. It belongs to U/North.

1461
01:49:18,546 --> 01:49:21,310
- 我知道是你杀了他 - 这是律师和客户之间的隐私
- I know you killed him. - It's attorney-client privilege.

1462
01:49:21,483 --> 01:49:25,146
凯伦，你看，现在，事情不该是这样的
See, now, that's just not the way to go here, Karen.

1463
01:49:25,320 --> 01:49:28,016
对于一个这么聪明的人来说，你有点儿 不知所措了，是不是？
For such a smart person, you really are lost, aren't you?

1464
01:49:28,190 --> 01:49:29,521
谈话结束
This conversation is over.

1465
01:49:29,691 --> 01:49:33,127
我不是你该除掉的人，我是你该收买的人
I'm not the guy that you kill. I'm the guy that you buy.

1466
01:49:33,295 --> 01:49:35,820
你他妈的瞎到连我是什么人都没看出来？
Are you so fucking blind you don't even see what I am?

1467
01:49:35,998 --> 01:49:39,490
我是你整个儿环节上最容易的一环 你还想做了我？
I'm the easiest part of your whole goddamn problem and you're gonna kill me?

1468
01:49:39,802 --> 01:49:42,930
你不知道我谁么？我是救火队员，我是跑腿的
Don't you know who I am? I'm a fixer. I'm a bagman.

1469
01:49:43,106 --> 01:49:46,507
我经手的人从顺手牵羊的主妇到 贪赃枉法的国会议员…
I do everything from shoplifting housewives to bent congressmen...

1470
01:49:46,676 --> 01:49:48,576
…你还想做了我？
...and you're gonna kill me?

1471
01:49:49,512 --> 01:49:52,345
你想要什么，凯伦？告诉我
What do you need, Karen? Lay it on me.

1472
01:49:52,516 --> 01:49:56,213
你想要枪支携带证明？还是想要关于 内线交易传票的警告
You want a carry permit? You want a heads-up on an insider-trading subpoena?

1473
01:49:56,387 --> 01:50:00,221
我8万块和一纸合同就把亚瑟卖了 你还想做了我？
I sold out Arthur for 80 grand and a contract and you're gonna kill me?

1474
01:50:01,725 --> 01:50:03,158
你想要什么？
What do you want?

1475
01:50:03,327 --> 01:50:04,851
我想要什么？
What do I want?

1476
01:50:05,029 --> 01:50:06,621
我要更多
I want more.

1477
01:50:07,131 --> 01:50:08,894
我要不干了
I want out.

1478
01:50:09,067 --> 01:50:11,695
有这个，我什么都要
And with this, I want everything.

1479
01:50:13,471 --> 01:50:14,699
开个价吧？
Is there a number?

1480
01:50:14,873 --> 01:50:16,465
我的要价是10
Ten is a number.

1481
01:50:16,641 --> 01:50:18,666
10？10什么？
Ten? Ten what?

1482
01:50:20,712 --> 01:50:22,202
1000万？
Ten million?

1483
01:50:22,380 --> 01:50:25,816
你觉得我上哪儿搞那1000万去？
Where do you think I'm gonna get 10 million dollars?

1484
01:50:26,385 --> 01:50:28,285
你知道这东西哪点好么？
You know what's great about this?

1485
01:50:28,454 --> 01:50:30,752
你看到结尾了吗？你看到谁签署的了吗？
Did you read it to the end? You see who signed it?

1486
01:50:31,324 --> 01:50:33,224
咱们一起进去问问丹・杰弗瑞…
Let's go in and ask Don Jeffries...

1487
01:50:33,392 --> 01:50:36,384
…看看他觉得这个价怎么样
...if he wants to pass the hat for a worthy cause.

1488
01:50:38,230 --> 01:50:40,630
还有很多需要商量的内容…
This would have to be a longer conversation...

1489
01:50:40,801 --> 01:50:42,928
…我们在别处继续谈
...and would have to take place somewhere else.

1490
01:50:43,103 --> 01:50:44,593
哪儿？我车里？
Where? My car?

1491
01:50:46,173 --> 01:50:47,197
好吧
All right.

1492
01:50:48,375 --> 01:50:51,401
简单点儿，5就行了
I'm gonna make it easy. Let's make it 5.

1493
01:50:51,578 --> 01:50:53,375
5百万我就能忘了亚瑟
Five and I'll forget about Arthur.

1494
01:50:55,750 --> 01:51:00,517
5百万容易些，好，5百万可以商量
Five is easier. Yeah, 5 is something that we could talk about.

1495
01:51:00,688 --> 01:51:04,419
好，还有5百万是为了忘记那468个…
Good. And then the other 5 is to forget about the 468 people...

1496
01:51:04,592 --> 01:51:06,685
…被你的除草剂害了的受害者
...that you knocked off with your weed killer.

1497
01:51:06,861 --> 01:51:09,227
就到这儿吧，我会和丹谈谈…
Let me finish up this meeting. I'll talk to Don...

1498
01:51:09,397 --> 01:51:11,991
我看起来是来谈判的吗？！
Do I look like I'm negotiating?!

1499
01:51:12,167 --> 01:51:13,498
凯伦？
Karen?

1500
01:51:14,203 --> 01:51:16,068
- 等一下 - 一切都好么？
- One second. - Everything okay?

1501
01:51:17,439 --> 01:51:18,428
好吧
Yes.

1502
01:51:19,441 --> 01:51:23,241
1000万美元，我选银行，离岸帐户，立即支付
Ten million dollars. Bank of my choosing. Offshore. Immediately.

1503
01:51:23,412 --> 01:51:24,538
- 好的 - 说一遍！
- Yes. - Say it!

1504
01:51:24,713 --> 01:51:28,581
1000万美元，你选帐户，马上就给
Ten million dollars, your account, the moment this meeting is through.

1505
01:51:28,752 --> 01:51:31,050
- 凯伦！大家都等着呢 - 我就来，丹
- Karen! Everyone's waiting. - I'm coming, Don.

1506
01:51:32,088 --> 01:51:33,453
成交了
You have a deal.

1507
01:51:34,024 --> 01:51:35,286
你被耍了
You're so fucked.

1508
01:51:35,625 --> 01:51:36,956
什么？
What?

1509
01:51:37,460 --> 01:51:39,325
- 你被耍了 - 你什么意思？
- You're fucked. - What do you mean?

1510
01:51:39,496 --> 01:51:41,726
- 猜猜看啊 - 有事吗？
- Take a wild guess. - Is there a problem?

1511
01:51:41,898 --> 01:51:44,594
- 我不明白 - 来让我拍一张“工作”照
- I don't understand. - Let me get a picture while I'm at it.

1512
01:51:44,769 --> 01:51:47,567
- 你不要钱吗？ - 自己留着吧，你会用得上的
- You don't want the money? - Keep the money. You'll need it.

1513
01:51:47,738 --> 01:51:49,330
这家伙烦着你了吗？
Is this fellow bothering you?

1514
01:51:49,507 --> 01:51:50,735
我烦着你了吗？
Am I bothering you?

1515
01:51:50,908 --> 01:51:54,935
凯伦，董事会都在里面等着呢 这到底出什么事了？你是谁？
Karen, I've got a board waiting in there. What the hell's going on? Who are you?

1516
01:51:55,112 --> 01:51:56,807
我是湿婆，死亡之神
I'm Shiva, the god of death.

1517
01:51:56,981 --> 01:52:00,610
罗！罗尼，让保安马上过来
Ron! Ronny, I need security out here immediately.

1518
01:52:01,520 --> 01:52:02,782
好的，这儿呢
All right. Here we go.

1519
01:52:02,954 --> 01:52:06,151
那个人，抓住那个人
That guy right there, stop him. Grab that guy.

1520
01:52:07,759 --> 01:52:10,489
- 你们干什么？ - 我们是纽约警局的侦探
- What are you doing? - We're detectives with the N.Y.P.D.

1521
01:52:10,662 --> 01:52:12,994
跟我们过来，我们会解释的
Come back with us and we'll explain everything.

1522
01:52:13,165 --> 01:52:16,430
看看她，看看她需不需要急救人员
Check on her. Make sure she doesn't need any medical attention.

1523
01:52:16,602 --> 01:52:18,763
你们进屋去，任何人都不许离开
You guys go into the ballroom. Nobody leaves.

1524
01:52:18,938 --> 01:52:20,701
所有出口都安排人把守
Have your guys cover every exit.

1525
01:52:20,873 --> 01:52:23,671
你们能不能解释下到底发生了什么事？
Will you please explain to me what's going on here?

1526
01:52:24,310 --> 01:52:25,675
你都录下了？
Did you get all that?

1527
01:52:25,845 --> 01:52:28,040
嗯，都录下了
Yeah. Got it.

1528
01:52:31,685 --> 01:52:34,518
- 你还好吧？ - 还好，就是得呼吸点儿新鲜空气
- You okay? - Yeah. Just gotta get some air.

1529
01:52:34,688 --> 01:52:36,178
好吧
Sure.

1530
01:52:36,557 --> 01:52:39,321
别乱跑，好吧？
Just stay close, okay?

1531
01:52:39,493 --> 01:52:40,721
好的
Okay.

1532
01:53:51,370 --> 01:53:53,201
我们去哪儿？
So, what are we doing?

1533
01:54:00,279 --> 01:54:02,270
开50块钱车资的距离
Give me 50 dollars' worth.

1534
01:54:04,150 --> 01:54:05,811
开就行了
Just drive.


